/* Some scripts to make 
potions and moving faster easy 
*/
?hp < 7 // I only use HP potions ngl 
  activate potion
//
?pickup | foe.distance >= 30 | foe.state < 0
  EquipL star
  EquipR tri

//
var stat = 6
// PRINT SCRIPTS 
>`0,@stat@,Name:@foe.name@
>`0,@stat+1@,Weakness:@DisplayWeak(foe)@
>`0,@stat+2@,State:@foe.state@
>`0,@stat+3@,time:@foe.time@ 
>`0,@stat+4@,Location:@loc.name@
>`0,@stat+5@,@item.left.state@:@item.left.time@
>`0,@stat+6@,
^@item.right.state@:@item.right.time@



